\lim_{x\to\infty} \frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}
x
\to + \infty
 \large \frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}\cdot \frac{\frac {1}{x}}{\frac{1}{\sqrt{x^2}}} =  \frac {\frac {5x^2}{x}}{\sqrt {\frac {7x^2}{x^2} - \frac 3{x^2}}} = \frac {5x}{\sqrt{7 - \frac 3{x^2}}} = \frac {5x}{7}
\lim_{x\to \infty} \frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}} =\lim_{x \to \infty}\frac {5x}{7}
\dfrac {5x}{7} \to +\infty
x \to \infty
\sqrt{x^2} = |x|
x^2
7x^2 - 3 < 9x^2
x
\frac{1}{7x^2 - 3} > \frac{1}{9x^2}
x
\frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2 - 3}} > \frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{9x^2}} = \frac{5x}{3}
x
3x\ge \sqrt{7x^2-3}\ge x
x
\lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}=\lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{5x^2}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}\frac{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}{\sqrt{7x^2-3}}=\lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{5x^2\sqrt{7x^2-3}}{7x^2-3}= \lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{5\sqrt{7x^2-3}}{7-\frac{3}{x^2}}
x\to\infty
\sqrt{7x^2-3}\to\infty,\frac{3}{x^2}\to{}0
\lim_{x\to\infty}\frac{5\sqrt{7x^2-3}}{7-\frac{3}{x^2}}=\frac{5\cdot\infty}{7-0}=\infty
